city: Notes. Rows 2-11 are directly from table 2. row 12 is inferred because the authors say that typha occurred in velocities less than 80cm/s. We didn't infer anything on the low end, because the absence there could be due to biotic competition with Phagmites which occurred in the low vel areas in this study.
